    <item>
      <title>About Me</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/en/o-mne/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//localhost:1313/en/o-mne/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;my name is Mirek Kučera. I was born in Prague in 2014 and I live in the Central Bohemian Region of the Czech Republic. My biggest hobby is K-pop.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I started dancing when I was five years old. I discovered K-pop thanks to the dance video game Just Dance and YouTube. The very first songs I learned were &lt;strong&gt;Boombayah&lt;/strong&gt; by BLACKPINK and &lt;strong&gt;Black Mamba&lt;/strong&gt; by aespa.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;There is no dance school in my town or the surrounding area that teaches K-pop, but that doesn’t bother me — I train and learn everything by myself at home. I spend all my free time practising and trying to improve.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
